body:
`range` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
    "$search": {
       "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
       "range": {
          "path": "<field-to-search>",
          "gt | gte": <value-to-search>,
          "lt | lte": <value-to-search>,
          "score": <score-options>
       }
    }
}
```

